Nutrient data for: CADBURY PICNIC CHOCOLATE BAR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210989277
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sugar, PEANUTS, glucose-fructose syrup, glucose syrup, WHEAT flour (with added calcium, iron, niacin, thiamin), dried grapes, palm oil, cocoa butter, cocoa mass, skimmed MILK powder, whey powder (from MILK), whey permeate powder (from MILK), rice flour, MILK fat, emulsifiers (E442, sunflower lecithin, E476, E471, SOYA lecithin), salt, BARLEY malt extract, maize flour, flavourings, anti-caking agent (E170), raising agents (E500, E503), MILK proteins. MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 14% MINIMUM.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN NUTS, EGG. Date available: 03/27/2018 Date last updated by company: 03/27/2018
